Class GraduateStudent

  • java.lang.Object
    • people.Person
      • people.PartTimeEmployee
        • people.GraduateStudent

  • public class GraduateStudent
extends PartTimeEmployee

    Contains graduate student attributes and algorithms to modify the attributes. Is considered a PartTimeEmployee.

    Depends on:

    Graduate student - obtains an undergraduate degree and continues further education.
